metadata.title: G Major - Rock
metadata.description:
this is a sweet track in G major or the Ionian mode
it's the first mode in the key of G
try first to locate all G's on the fretboard
then build your major scale on each
after that try to connect all shapes
then listen well to the progression you will feel the happy sound of the major scale
try to build melodies and phrases on the G major scale

feel free to post your jams on the group and only shortlisted jams will be approved.

have fun and keep rocking!~~ :)
